values: Hello. Hello. Hello....In There. In There. In There.........is no one around anymore. Neither am i. Hit me up on Myspace if anyone is looking for me!

Going

He was looking for a place so we can move in together and we got one. We move in tomorrow. Of corse its only for about two or three moths but its a start huh? I guess while he and i are looking for jobs.....weird...its just weird.
Am i giving up my careere my potential and whole life again for someone who may not even deserve it??? I dont even knggles::

Heh......kidding....

Why does this happen!?!?!?!!? Im like in such an emotional state. Ive never been this emotional befor. Even with all of the shit thats happen fro back in the day. grrrrrrrrr........RAWWWWWWWWWRR!

heard the new BSB song. I like it. DOnt love it but i like it. Nick has a great voice. Aj's talent is not demonstrated in this one but i know its there....heh.

This baby is working my nerves. ITs so weired for someone who wanted to have ten to not be able to support one. Thats cuz shes not mine! Im going down with GIo to watch the game tonight and i didnt wnat to......
